description: The NanoPi Zero2 is a compact single-board computer designed around the Rockchip RK3528A processor. This device is available with an optional metal case and provides a Gigabit Ethernet port, as well as optional Wi-Fi connectivity via an M.2 slot. Powered by a quad-core ARM Cortex-A53 CPU running up to 2.0 GHz, the NanoPi Zero2 is […]
title: NanoPi Zero2 with Gigabit Ethernet and Optional Wi-Fi Connectivity via M.2 Slot
